rdination are key to prevailing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW CHAMPIONS EVERY MONTH</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/915580/extras/c2ef0faae639f9b0b179b5ae67b36f7c.poster.avif?t=1749833919\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/915580/extras/c2ef0faae639f9b0b179b5ae67b36f7c.webm?t=1749833919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/915580/extras/c2ef0faae639f9b0b179b5ae67b36f7c.mp4?t=1749833919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In case the base pool of 250+ Champions is not enough for you, new characters with unique playstyles and skills are added every month. With new combos and theorycrafting possibilities, you have total freedom to build the ultimate team.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >25-VS-25-PLAYER GUILD WARS</h2>Form a Guild, recruit members, prepare a plan, carry out your strategy, and invade the enemy Guild Hall. May your Guild's banner fly high all across the Multiverse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/915580/extras/984135dcc413441319a78c4cfa5e47fc.poster.avif?t=1749833919\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/915580/extras/984135dcc413441319a78c4cfa5e47fc.webm?t=1749833919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/915580/extras/984135dcc413441319a78c4cfa5e47fc.mp4?t=1749833919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
